HEADWORD: Perissad
<hw>Per"is*sad</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ odd, from
<?/ over.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Odd; not even; -- said of
elementary substances and of radicals whose valence is not divisible by
two without a remainder. Contrasted with <contr>artiad</contr>.</def>
<mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

